{"tid":1013260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三名警員調查毒品案作虛假陳述候判","createTime":"2019-02-08T08:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T15:01:49.000Z","uid":37554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1f4374bfbcb70ff64f0272e53d027fe1208f9b63","tid":1013260,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:08:20.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】三名警務人員在調查一宗毒品案時作虛假陳述，被裁定一項作出傾向並意圖妨礙司法公正罪罪名成立。辯方律師求情時指，此案有別一般同類型案件，希望法庭以小懲大戒方式處理。<br />\n<br />\n三名被告在親友陪同下扺達觀塘法院大樓聽取判刑。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師呈上多封求情信，指三人均為警隊服務多年，多次獲得上司讚揚，這宗案件只是技術性犯錯。辯方律師又表示，這宗案件有別於近期的同樣牽涉警員的案件，被告並沒有以警察身分作出包庇或用警棍毆打途人等行為，希望法庭可以考慮案件的獨特性，以緩刑取代即時監禁。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，三名警員在2016年一宗毒品案中影響證據，夾口供指控一名男子藏毒並管有吸食工具。"},{"pid":"28f0f1f36458ac63efcd492b299ea3a0f98fceb3","tid":1013260,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=336902&amp;hot=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D336902%26hot%3D1&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1IVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=666c30ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D336902%26hot%3D1&h=e0859e68\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=336902&amp;hot=1</a>"},{"pid":"ff3329196f962e92c71a5ab62037c3aa1cf8a363","tid":1013260,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"所以話啲律師真係讀撚壞書，荒誕到將講大話扭曲成技術性犯錯"},{"pid":"5dd760fd2dce091c65a7ac9d459499b26e8bbeb1","tid":1013260,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"帽子戲法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b8b2b2f1c091a24560693914261fde42c766af","tid":1013260,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor